			Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convDonanSearch02, idDonan)
		end
	end
end

function Start()
	idDonan = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(sDonanFollower)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idDonan) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idDonan) then
		local idFollowerOwner = Hydra.ActorGetFollowTarget(idDonan)
		
		-- Play different line if player did earlier OPT conversation
		if Hydra.IsPlayerVariableSet(idFollowerOwner, "EldhaimeCompletedOPT08") then
			Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convEnterBarracksAlt, idFollowerOwner)
		else	
			Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convEnterBarracks, idFollowerOwner)
		end
	end
end

	idTraversalMarker = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "TRAVERSAL_MARKER")[1]

	end
	
	Hydra.EventSend("Start_SecretDoor_Vignette")
	
end
